00214         inline void Add(const std::string& key, const T& value)
00215         {
00216                 aiString* new_keys = new aiString[mNumProperties + 1];
00217                 aiMetadataEntry* new_values = new aiMetadataEntry[mNumProperties + 1];
00218

00220                 {

00236     template<typename T>
00237     inline 
00238     bool Set( unsigned index, const std::string& key, const T& value ) {
00239         // In range assertion
00240         if ( index >= mNumProperties ) {
00241             return false;
00242         }
00243 
00244         // Ensure that we have a valid key.
00245         if ( key.empty() ) {
00246             return false;
00247         }
00248 
00249         // Set metadata key
00250         mKeys[index] = key;
00251 
00252         // Set metadata type
00253         mValues[index].mType = GetAiType(value);
00254         // Copy the given value to the dynamic storage
00255         mValues[index].mData = new T(value);
00256 
00257         return true;
00258     }

00260     template<typename T>
00261     inline 
00262     bool Get( unsigned index, T& value ) {
00263         // In range assertion
00264         if ( index >= mNumProperties ) {
00265             return false;
00266         }
00267 
00268         // Return false if the output data type does
00269         // not match the found value's data type
00270         if ( GetAiType( value ) != mValues[ index ].mType ) {
00271             return false;
00272         }
00273 
00274         // Otherwise, output the found value and
00275         // return true
00276         value = *static_cast<T*>(mValues[index].mData);
00277 
00278         return true;
00279     }
